Dear Dale,

I don't know if it appeared anywhere earlier, but the result for an
arbitrary poset is Proposition 8.4 in Birkedal, Mogelberg, Schwinghammer
and Stovring's paper "First steps in synthetic domain theory:
step-indexing in the topos of trees".

http://www.cs.au.dk/~birke/papers/sgdt-journal.pdf

Paul



